	<sectionClass_s>no-margin-top</sectionClass_s>
	<sectionContent_html>&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s probably safe for me to assume that you&amp;rsquo;ve watched a Hollywood movie or two in your time, right?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Chances are that at least one of those movies featured a trust fund baby somewhere in the plot. You know the character I&amp;rsquo;m talking about. It&amp;rsquo;s always an unemployed yet suspiciously rich kid with expensive sports car and overpriced designer clothes. And lots of very expensive hobbies for some reason.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Be honest. You were still a bit jealous of that trust fund kid, weren&amp;rsquo;t you? Just a little.&lt;/p&gt;</sectionContent_html>
