	<objectId>3a8b6ed5-cf13-b266-196a-1f7150efa995</objectId>
	<internal-name>Sec 2</internal-name>
	<sectionClass_s>no-margin-bottom</sectionClass_s>
	<file-name>3a8b6ed5-cf13-b266-196a-1f7150efa995.xml</file-name>
	<sectionContent_html>&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Generational wealth is a vital financial tool for building true, lasting wealth within families. Here are our top three tips for building your own family&amp;rsquo;s financial legacy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="text--md" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: var(--text-md); font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;1. Fall in love with saving and investing&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Investing your money is an important tool for building wealth not only for your family but for your immediate future as well. If you&amp;rsquo;re not sure how to get started investing, we&amp;rsquo;ve&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="background-color: transparent;" href="/articles/2021/3/how-to-start-investing"&gt;written a handy guide here&lt;/a&gt;. Or simply ask your Velocity Club relationship consultant for advice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Becoming a savvy investor is a critical first step to creating significant generational wealth. There are many routes you can take to building your own successful investment portfolio. For example, you might decide to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="background-color: transparent;" href="/articles/2020/10/residential-property-the-ins-and-outs"&gt;put your money into property&lt;/a&gt;, or you could start your own business. Perhaps you&amp;rsquo;d rather invest your money in the stock market. Or maybe your strategy involves a bit of each. Whichever option you choose, the goal here is to grow your money, in order to grow your overall wealth.&lt;/p&gt;</sectionContent_html>
