	<internal-name>Callout right one</internal-name>
	<call_out_content_html>&lt;h2 class="title--md no-margin-top" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: 32px; margin-top: 0px; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-style: italic; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Another option is to save money for your children&amp;rsquo;s education. Education is something that nobody can ever take away from you, but it&amp;rsquo;s also expensive and consequently, many people miss out on opportunities simply because they don&amp;rsquo;t have the education to pursue them.&lt;/h2&gt;</call_out_content_html>
