	<objectGroupId>2f71</objectGroupId>
	<objectId>2f7199cb-e438-2fbf-ba79-e52d9e1097bc</objectId>
	<file-name>2f7199cb-e438-2fbf-ba79-e52d9e1097bc.xml</file-name>
	<internal-name>Sec 3</internal-name>
	<sectionClass_s>no-margin-bottom</sectionClass_s>
	<sectionContent_html>&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Of course, we understand that&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="background-color: transparent;" href="/articles/2021/2/bouncing-back-from-the-pandemic"&gt;things are tough&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;right now and saving money can be difficult. The good news is that we know what you&amp;rsquo;re going through and we&amp;rsquo;ve got the resources and the experts to help you with all the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="background-color: transparent;" href="/articles/2020/10/in-the-spirit-of-halloween-here-are-3-money-tricks-to-avoid"&gt;financial tips&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;you need to get a reasonable investment portion out of&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="background-color: transparent;" href="/articles/2021/5/working-from-home-here-s-how-you-could-pay-less-tax"&gt;your income every month&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="text--md" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: var(--text-md); font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;2. Protect your wealth and create a will&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Life insurance policies allow you to provide for your family in the event that you unexpectedly pass away. And therefore, it&amp;rsquo;s a tool to protect the wealth that you have been working so hard to build. For that reason, insurance is a critical tool in planning for your family&amp;rsquo;s financial needs. A decent policy will ensure that your family isn&amp;rsquo;t forced into undesirable living conditions if you&amp;rsquo;re unable to provide for them.&lt;/p&gt;</sectionContent_html>
	<createdDate>2021-09-01T14:22:15.361Z</createdDate>
