	<call_out_content_html>&lt;h2 class="title--md no-margin-top" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: 32px; margin-top: 0px; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-style: italic; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;In order to ensure that the generational wealth that you&amp;rsquo;ve begun building is continued and built on by your children, you need to talk to them about your philosophy for the future.&lt;/h2&gt;</call_out_content_html>
