	<internal-name>Conclusion</internal-name>
	<sectionClass_s>no-margin-top</sectionClass_s>
	<file-name>3f187fbe-b443-e3ab-4d6d-7f0925a346ca.xml</file-name>
	<sectionContent_html>&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Have an open, transparent and ongoing conversation with them about how you created the wealth, what sacrifices you made to get there, and the purposes you envision for the wealth you&amp;rsquo;ve started building. By ensuring that the next generation understands the way in which your wealth is structured, you can ensure that they are equipped to receive and manage it responsibly in the future.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="text--md" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: var(--text-md); font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Conclusion&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Building generational wealth is a fantastic legacy project to ensure that your family is properly taken care of. Today, we&amp;rsquo;ve discussed the three main elements of generational wealth building. Those were - learning how to invest your money, taking out life insurance and drafting a Will, and finally, having an ongoing conversation with your children about how you want the family&amp;rsquo;s money to be managed when you pass away.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;We want to empower you with all of the information you need to succeed in your wealth-building journey. If you&amp;rsquo;d like to set up a call with one of our relationship consultants, you can do so&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="background-color: transparent; color: var(--color-black);" data-tf-slider="Sgz7HGMv" data-tf-width="550" data-tf-hidden="utm_source=CTA,utm_medium=website,utm_campaign=velocityclub_site,utm_term=,utm_content=" data-tf-loaded="true"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and if you&amp;rsquo;d like to learn how to start investing, you can join our free 20-minute Masterclass with Financial Journalist, Arabile Gumede,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="background-color: transparent;" href="https://event.webinarjam.com/register/148/6kxyyt89" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</sectionContent_html>
